    {
      "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-80aa-a8c1-ed44c5ef1e48",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors evaluate their model using 4 metrics: Normalized Discount Cumulative Gain & Maean Average Precision (Offline evaluation) and Novelty & Diversity (online evaluation). ",
